<h2 id="placeAnAd">How to place an advertisement</h2>
<p>The fastest and easiest way to place an advertisement with us is via email at <a href='mailto:"tt-ads@mit.edu"'><em>tt-ads@mit.edu</em></a>.
	We need the following information from you:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Desired publication date(s)</li>
  <li>Desired size</li>
  <% if @advertiser_type == :mit %>
    <li>Contact information</li>
    <li>MIT Account Number</li>
  <% else %>
    <li>Contact information, including mailing address</li>
    <li>Billing preference (check or credit card &mdash; Please do NOT include credit card numbers in your email)</li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<p>
  The deadline for advertisement submission, including artwork, is at 5 p.m. 3 days before the publication date.
	Artwork should be submitted either in image or PDF format; all images should be at least 220dpi.
	Late advertisements will incur a <%= @late_fee_percentage %>% surcharge.
      </p>
<p>
  If you are unsure about any of these items, please <a href='mailto:"tt-ads@mit.edu"'>email us</a>.
      </p>
<% if @advertiser_type == :mit %>
  <p><i>Note: Information on this page is for MIT Departments.
